      "name": "Construct stiffness QoI comparison — non-cannulated",
      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared against N=11 experimental measurements. Mean absolute percent error 4.2%; E/uval = 0.87, satisfying the pre-established acceptance criterion of E/uval < 1.96. A UQ campaign covering material property and boundary-condition parameters was executed prior to this comparison; Sobol first-order indices documented in technical report TR-2023-NC-01 identify cortical modulus as the dominant sensitivity driver."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/validation/vr-yield-force-noncannulated",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Yield force QoI comparison — non-cannulated",
      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force compared against experimental values across both laboratories. Mean absolute percent error 6.8%; E/uval = 1.34, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Uncertainty quantification results (Monte Carlo, n=1000 samples) are summarized in TR-2023-NC-01 Section 4."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/validation/vr-force-40mm-noncannulated",
