      "name": "Force at 40 mm displacement QoI comparison — non-cannulated",
      "description": "FEA-predicted force at 40 mm displacement compared against experimental values. Mean absolute percent error 7.1%; E/uval = 1.61, within acceptance bounds. Full sensitivity analysis results are embedded in the UQ campaign report but are not linked via a structured hasSensitivityAnalysis node in this package."
    }
