      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified with literature support; contact formulation documented. Required Gradation 3: model form uncertainty quantified or bounded.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity selected for Ti-6Al-4V based on published tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrange contact with friction coefficient 0.2 (literature range 0.15–0.25) employed. Model form uncertainty bounded by comparing against a linear-elastic idealization; plasticity model shown necessary for post-yield QoIs."
