      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.34), and force at 40 mm (1.61); all below the pre-specified threshold of 1.96. Validation uncertainty uval composed of experimental measurement uncertainty and simulation numerical uncertainty per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.4."
